column2: SELECT top #   g.flags,     dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&BADSKY),  --should not be zero   dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&SATURATED), dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&NODEBLEND), dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&LOCAL_EDGE), dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&SATUR_CENTER), dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&MAYBE_CR)        into MyDB.temp from MyDB.lowz1#_v5_short AS m   OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n   LEFT OUTER join dr1#.Galaxy as g On g.objid=n.objid
